413
00:43:02,367 --> 00:43:03,200
This is Chiyomi?

414
00:43:03,267 --> 00:43:05,700
I heard she's an online novelist.

415
00:43:06,467 --> 00:43:08,200
Now he knows!

416
00:43:08,333 --> 00:43:10,567
Minami can't read it!

417
00:43:10,633 --> 00:43:13,500
Mom is gonna file
a missing person's report!

418
00:43:14,833 --> 00:43:17,000
I know you're the giant!

419
00:43:17,933 --> 00:43:23,300
The One Inch Princess went
to Cape Akebono and grew back.

420
00:43:23,367 --> 00:43:26,033
It's like a secret love affair!

421
00:43:26,567 --> 00:43:29,300
Oh, God, please grow me back!

